Coding Style
============

Maximal line length is 80 columns. (I hate endless lines.)

Indent by 4 spaces. No tabulators. (Because width limit.)

Use ISO C 99 languge and POSIX or Single UNIX Specification functions.
(Portability.)

Opening parentheses remains at the end of line. (Consistency.)

Each non-static function has to have a prefix. `isds_' prefix for public
functions, `_isds_' for internal functions shared between objects. (Not to
polute name space, especially with static linkage.)

Internal functions shared beetween objects but not in public API have to have
`_hidden' marker on function definition to exclude the symbol from exporting
to symbol table. (Run-time optimization.)

